Prototype multiple-fluid solver for 2016-2017 MPC Masterclass
Based on the paper "Multiple-fluid SPH Simulation Using a Mixture Model" by Ren et al. (Available at http://gamma.cs.unc.edu/SPH_MULTI_FLUIDS/TOG2014.pdf)
Initial code from https://github.com/finallyjustice/sphfluid/tree/master/SPH_CPU_3D_v1
